name: Cute Honey 2
description:
Cute Honey 2 is a casual strategy game, how to get the liquid into the cup is the core of the game.

  • Two cute and sexy girls, which one do you prefer?
  • Fun and creative paintbrush game
  • Thirty new levels for you to play
  • Secrets of girls, a variety of sex positions, all up to you to explore

More exquisite achievements and background display pictures are waiting for you to experience.
